        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName>Down, Beckenham, Kent</placeName>
                    <date>April 4, 1872</date>
                    <salute>Dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I thank you most sincerely for your kindness. You must not think of trying until you feel some inclination and strength for the task. I have written to Mr. Cooper (188 Strand) to send you the blocks.<ref target="#foot.f1"/></p>
<p>My dear Sir | yours very faithfully | Ch. Darwin</p>
<p>P.S. I may as well add my address for parcels viz. C. Darwin Esq. | Orpington Station | South Eastern Railway</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

            
            
        </div>

        

        

